      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute gem. I\u2019ve taken such good care of her, and she\u2019s still looking and driving like she just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s honestly in pristine condition\u2014spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the showroom price tag, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
