      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a peerless example of high-performance engineering, this specimen features a naturally aspirated flat-six engine delivering linear power through a lightning-fast dual-clutch transmission. The chassis is anchored by an adaptive damping system and reinforced multi-link rear suspension, ensuring zero compliance under heavy lateral loads. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with no evidence of road rash or thermal cycling on the composite panels. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative; the braking system utilizes six-piston monoblock calipers with ventilated rotors for exceptional heat dissipation, and the intake plenum remains free of carbon buildup. This vehicle has been maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the integrity of every seal and bushing to original factory tolerances. A true turn-key acquisition for the collector who demands mechanical transparency and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
