      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade example that defines the term 'mint.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, showing absolutely zero paint imperfections, door dings, or road rash. The factory deep-gloss finish remains preserved under a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery retains its original matte texture with no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty liners since day one. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. It drives as tightly as it did on the showroom floor, with no rattles, leaks, or vibrations. Included are all original keys, the full owner\u2019s manual set, and a comprehensive binder of service records. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
